Company Overview of Mechel Mining OAO



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mechel Mining OAO, through its subsidiaries, manufactures, markets, and exports metallurgical coals for steel companies in the Russian Federation and internationally. It produces coking coal concentrates, anthracites, PCI, thermal coal, iron ore concentrates, coke, and other coking and chemical products. The company also manufactures coke gas and various chemicals, including benzene, toluene, solvent, naphthalene, ammonium sulphate, resins, and other products. It supplies its products through its international sales network. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Moscow, Russian Federation with production assets in the United States and the Russian Federation. Mechel Mining ...
Mechel Mining OAO, through its subsidiaries, manufactures, markets, and exports metallurgical coals for steel companies in the Russian Federation and internationally. It produces coking coal concentrates, anthracites, PCI, thermal coal, iron ore concentrates, coke, and other coking and chemical products. The company also manufactures coke gas and various chemicals, including benzene, toluene, solvent, naphthalene, ammonium sulphate, resins, and other products. It supplies its products through its international sales network. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Moscow, Russian Federation with production assets in the United States and the Russian Federation. Mechel Mining OAO operates as a subsidiary of Mechel OAO.
