Mechel Mining OAO Key Developments

South Kuzbass PAO Amends Loan Contract with Mechel-Mining OAO
Apr 13 17
South Kuzbass PAO signed an interested-party deal an additional agreement to a loan contract with Mechel-Mining OAO (the borrower). The maturity is June 17, 2022. The deal value is RUB 2,795,926,191.74.


Korshunovsky Gok Amends Loan Contract with Mechel-Mining
Feb 7 17
On January 16, 2017 Korshunovsky GOK PAO (the Irkutsk region) signed an interested-party deal - an additional agreement to a loan contract with Mechel-Mining OAO (the borrower). The additional agreement changes the interest rate, the loan amount and extends term of the deal. Term of the deal: through May 6, 2022. The deal value: RUB 629,738,730.


South Kuzbass Amends Loan Contract with Mechel Mining OAO
Jan 27 17
On December 27, 2016 South Kuzbass PAO (the Kemerovo region) signed an interested-party deal - an additional agreement to a loan contract with Mechel-Mining OAO (the borrower). The maturity date is August 23, 2022 and the deal value of RUB 2,121,338,808.66. The deal was approved by the Board of Directors on December 23, 2016.


