Mechel OAO Buyback
OLI recorded this information on 6/18/2013


Company:
Mechel OAO


Buyback:
MTL buyback


$Amount Authorized:
$100,000,000 


Buyback Details:
Mechel OAO (NYSE:MTL), one of the leading Russian mining and metals companies, announces the decision of the company's Board of Directors to authorize the buy back of up to $100 million of ADRs representing Mechel OAO's common shares.


	
	     Mechel is a steel and mining company engaged in producing and selling mining products used in the production of steel, primarily coking coal, iron ore and nickel. Co. is also engaged in producing and selling semi-finished steel products; carbon and specialty long products; carbon and stainless flat products; and value-added downstream metal products including hardware, stampings and forgings. Co. also produces coke, both for internal use and for sales to third parties. Co. operations are organized along three business segments: the mining segment, the steel segment, and the power segment. Co. sells its products within Russia and foreign markets.    
