			Company Description 


			Mechel PAO is a holding company, which engages in the mining and production of coal and steel, iron core, and nickel products. It operates through the following business segments: Steel, Mining and Power. The Steel segment comprises steel and steel products. The Mining segment comprises coal, iron o...
		


                Mechel PAO is a holding company, which engages in the mining and production of coal and steel, iron core, and nickel products. It operates through the following business segments: Steel, Mining and Power. The Steel segment comprises steel and steel products. The Mining segment comprises coal, iron ore and coke. The Power comprises electricity and heat power. Mechel was founded on March 19, 2003 and is headquartered in Moscow, Russia.
            




