Mechel



@PAOMechel


Mechel (NYSE:MTL) - $MTL - is a global mining and steel company, headquartered in Moscow, Russia. Mechel produces coal, iron ore, steel, ferroalloys and power.



            Moscow

      



 
    mechel.com
  




